headline: 2 High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy With $300 and Hold Forever
summary: Investing in dividend stocks can be a great way to set up a durable income stream.  The best ones can provide you with stable and growing recurring dividend income that can last a lifetime.  Realty Income (NYSE: O) and Mid-America Apartment Communities (NYSE: MAA) have been very durable dividend stocks over the decades.
